> 赛后总结

## 流水账

#### 0-5min
看完题, 定了顺序	
题目难度应该是 :

> 2        1        3        4

#### 5-20min

写完了T2。

#### 20-30min

对T2进行静态查错

#### 30-50min

想了T3的《正解》，但证明不会。

#### 50-75min

写完了T3的《正解》，过了样例

#### 75-90min

谢了T3的对拍

#### 90-100min

对拍出错了。	

是  对拍   出错了

#### 100-101min

光速修对拍，原因是在生成 `l`和`r`时，忘了交换大小。。。

#### 101-102min

对拍出错了。	

这次是对拍出  错   了。

#### 102-115min

开始质疑T3《正解》。	

然后看了看 Hack 数据。	

但是貌似我修不好T3。	

然后进行了《正确率分析》	

用对拍算了一下，大概只有 $60 - 70 \% $的正确率。

#### 115-120min

乱搞T4。	

#### 120-130min

读懂了第一题

#### 130-150min

写完了正解。

#### 150-175min

开始瞎搞打表。。。	



<details>

step1
```cpp
#include <cstdio>
#include <iostream>
#include <algorithm>
using namespace std;
const int MAXN = 6;
const char table[10] = {0, 'I', 'V', 'X', 'L', 'C', 'D', 'M'};

int n, cnt, a[MAXN], t[MAXN * 2];

void change (int x) {
	cnt = 0;
	while (x) {
		a[++cnt] = x % 10;
		x /= 10;
	}
}

void print (int x) {
	for (int i = cnt; i >= 1; i--) {
		if (i == 1) {
			if (a[i] == 4) {
				printf ("VI");
				t[1]++, t[2]++;
			} 
			if (a[i] == 5) {
				printf ("V");
				t[2]++;
			}
			if (a[i] == 9) {
				printf ("IX");
				t[1]++, t[3]++;
			}
			if (a[i] <= 3) {
				for (int j = 1; j <= a[i]; j++) {
					printf ("I");
					t[1]++;
				}
			}
			if (a[i] > 5 && a[i] < 9) {
				printf ("V");
				t[2]++;
				for (int j = 6; j <= a[i]; j++) {
					printf ("I");
					t[1]++;
				}
			}
		}
		if (i == 2) {
			if (a[i] == 4) {
				printf ("LX");
				t[4]++, t[3]++;
			} 
			if (a[i] == 5) {
				printf ("L");
				t[4]++;
			}
			if (a[i] == 9) {
				printf ("XC");
				t[3]++, t[5]++;
			}
			if (a[i] <= 3) {
				for (int j = 1; j <= a[i]; j++) {
					printf ("X");
					t[3]++;
				}
			}
			if (a[i] > 5 && a[i] < 9) {
				printf ("L");
				t[4]++;
				for (int j = 6; j <= a[i]; j++) {
					printf ("X");
					t[3]++;
				}
			}
		}
		if (i == 3) {
			if (a[i] == 4) {
				printf ("DC");
				t[6]++, t[5]++;
			} 
			if (a[i] == 5) {
				printf ("D");
				t[6]++;
			}
			if (a[i] == 9) {
				printf ("CM");
				t[5]++, t[7]++;
			}
			if (a[i] <= 3) {
				for (int j = 1; j <= a[i]; j++) {
					printf ("C");
					t[5]++;
				}
			}
			if (a[i] > 5 && a[i] < 9) {
				printf ("D");
				t[6]++;
				for (int j = 6; j <= a[i]; j++) {
					printf ("C");
					t[5]++;
				}
			}
		}
		if (i == 4) {
			for (int j = 1; j <= a[i]; j++) {
				printf ("M");
				t[7]++;
			}
		}
	}
	printf ("\n");
}

int main () {
	freopen ("table.in", "w", stdout);
	n = 3500;
	for (int i = 1; i <= n; i++) {
		change (i);
		print (i);
	}
	for (int i = 1; i <= 7; i++) {
		if (t[i] != 0) {
			printf ("%c %d\n", table[i], t[i]);
		}
	}
	return 0;
}
```

step2

```cpp
#include <cstdio>
#include <cstring>
#include <iostream>
#include <algorithm>
using namespace std;

int t[10][3500];
char s[100];

int main () {
	freopen ("table.in", "r", stdin);
	freopen ("table.out", "w", stdout);
	for (int i = 1; i <= 3500; i++) {
		scanf ("%s", s + 1);
		int len = strlen (s + 1);
		for (int j = 1; j <= 7; j++) t[j][i] = t[j][i - 1];
		for (int j = 1; j <= len; j++) {
			if (s[j] == 'I') t[1][i]++;
			if (s[j] == 'V') t[2][i]++;
			if (s[j] == 'X') t[3][i]++;
			if (s[j] == 'L') t[4][i]++;
			if (s[j] == 'C') t[5][i]++;
			if (s[j] == 'D') t[6][i]++;
			if (s[j] == 'M') t[7][i]++;
		}
	}
	for (int i = 1; i <= 7; i++) {
		printf ("const int t%d[3505] = {0, ", i);
		for (int j = 1; j < 3500; j++) {
			printf ("%d, ", t[i][j]);
		}
		printf ("%d", t[i][3500]);
		printf ("};\n");
	}
	return 0;
}
```

</details>



然后。。。	

<font color = red>10k code 警告</font>

#### 175-200min

开始检查细节。

#### result

OJ: `100+100+79+29=308`	

Lemon: `0+100+60+10=170`	

打表代码太长结果找不到源程序。	

然后重新交了一份正解。	

Lemon:`100+100+60+10=270`







## summary

不该写T1的打表。	

花了30min，结果还是徒劳。	

反而T4的暴力翻车了。。。	

T3其实是接近正解，但是没把特殊情况讨论出来。	



## 教训

有把握的题就不要写得太`zuo`，把时间留给难题。

#### T2

<details>

```cpp

#include <cstdio>
#include <cstring>
#include <iostream>
#include <algorithm>
using namespace std;
const int MAXLEN = 2e5 + 5;

int n, len;
char a[MAXLEN], b[MAXLEN];

bool check (int l1, int r1, int l2, int r2) {
	bool flag = 1;
	for (int i = l1, j = l2; i <= r1 && j <= r2; i++, j++) {
		if (a[i] != b[j]) {
			flag = 0;
			break;
		}
	}
	if (flag == 1) {
		return 1;
	}
	if ((r1 - l1 + 1) % 2 == 1) {
		return 0;
	}
	int mid = ((r1 - l1) + 1) >> 1;
	return ((check (l1, l1 + mid - 1, l2, l2 + mid - 1) && check (r1 - mid + 1, r1, r2 - mid + 1, r2)) || 
			(check (l1, l1 + mid - 1, r2 - mid + 1, r2) && check (r1 - mid + 1, r1, l2, l2 + mid - 1)));
}

int main () {
	freopen ("string.in", "r", stdin);
	freopen ("string.out", "w", stdout);
	scanf ("%d", &n);
	while (n--) {
		scanf ("%s", a + 1);	
		scanf ("%s", b + 1);
		len = strlen (a + 1);
		if (check (1, len, 1, len)) {
			printf ("YES\n");
		} else printf ("NO\n");
	}
	return 0;
}
```

#### T3



<details>

```cpp
#include <cstdio>
#include <cstring>
#include <iostream>
#include <algorithm>
#define int long long
using namespace std;
const int MAXN = 1e5 + 5;

int n, ans, tmp;
struct node {
    int l, r;
} a[MAXN];
bool cmp(node x, node y) { return (x.l == y.l) ? x.r < y.r : x.l < y.l; }

int Max(int x, int y) { return (x > y) ? x : y; }

int Min(int x, int y) { return (x < y) ? x : y; }

int Tot(int x) { return (x < 0) ? 0 : x; }

int sl[MAXN], sr[MAXN], tl[MAXN], tr[MAXN];

signed main() {
    //	freopen ("homework.in", "r", stdin);
    //	freopen ("homework.out", "w", stdout);
    scanf("%lld", &n);
    for (int i = 1; i <= n; i++) {
        scanf("%lld %lld", &a[i].l, &a[i].r);
    }
    sort(a + 1, a + 1 + n, cmp);
    memset(sl, 0, sizeof(sl));
    memset(sr, 0x3f, sizeof(sr));
    memset(tl, 0, sizeof(tl));
    memset(tr, 0x3f, sizeof(tr));
    for (int i = 1; i <= n; i++) {
        sl[i] = Max(sl[i - 1], a[i].l);
        sr[i] = Min(sr[i - 1], a[i].r);
    }
    for (int i = n; i >= 1; i--) {
        tl[i] = Max(tl[i + 1], a[i].l);
        tr[i] = Min(tr[i + 1], a[i].r);
    }
    sl[0] = tl[n + 1] = 0;
    sr[0] = tr[n + 1] = -1;
    for (int i = 0; i <= n; i++) {
        tmp = Tot(sr[i] - sl[i] + 1) + Tot(tr[i + 1] - tl[i + 1] + 1);
        ans = Max(ans, tmp);
    }
    for (int i = 1; i <= n; i++) {
        ans = Max(ans, a[i].r - a[i].l + 1 + Tot (Min (sr[i - 1], tr[i + 1]) - Max (sl[i - 1], tl[i + 1]) + 1));
    }
    printf("%lld\n", ans);
    return 0;
}
```

#### T4

<details>

```cpp
#include <cstdio>
#include <iostream>
#include <algorithm>
using namespace std;
const int MAXN = 1e6 + 5;

int n, dp[30][3], ans;
char s[MAXN];

int Max (int x, int y) {
	return (x > y) ? x : y;
}

int main () {
	scanf ("%d", &n);
	scanf ("%s", s + 1);
	for (int i = 0; i < 26; i++) {
		for (int j = 0; j < 26; j++) {
			dp[j][0] = 0xcfcfcfcf;
			dp[j][1] = 0;
		}
		for (int pos = 1; pos <= n; pos++) {
			if (s[pos] == i + 'a') {
				for (int j = 0; j < 26; j++) {
					dp[j][0]++, dp[j][1]++;
					ans = Max (ans, dp[j][0]);
				}
			} else {
				int j = s[pos] - 'a';
				dp[j][0] = dp[j][1] - 1;
				dp[j][1] = Max (0, dp[j][1] - 1);
				ans = Max (ans, dp[j][0]);
			}
		}
	}
	printf ("%d\n", ans);
	return 0;
}
```
